  "instructions": [
    "Combine oats, sugar, and vanilla extract in a bowl. Mix until well combined.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together egg yolks and lemon juice.",
    "In a small saucepan, melt butter over medium heat.",
    "Pour the butter mixture into the oats mixture and mix until well combined.",
    "Gradually pour in heavy cream, whisking until smooth.",
    "Add the egg yolk mixture to the oats mixture and mix until well combined.",
    "Pour the mixture into the cannoli shells.",
    "Chill in the refrigerator for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Serve chilled, dust with powdered sugar.",
    "Top with blueberries and lemon zest."
